                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260511-128-victim727 t18260511-128-viclabel741"></join>. I had those four brushes in my shop, but I do not know that I had seen them on the 28th of April - the officer brought them that day; I looked and saw a peg was empty, which had had brushes on it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260511-128-person728">
